{"tid":327296,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇出碟歌曝光】蘇打綠青峰唱《只有可以》","createTime":"2017-07-18T15:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T15:55:52.000Z","uid":14730,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"936a9dd7e760b26d45db653183d43685085611a1","tid":327296,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/224806_b0e77a5cc0b4d16ba385f6578a4684f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F224806_b0e77a5cc0b4d16ba385f6578a4684f2.png&h=64f9a1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次青峰演繹的《只有可以》之前一直都未有正式發行，僅在演唱會中唱過。而青峰會選擇唱《只有可以》，是為了可以為一班「打工仔」粉絲打氣。他亦在Facebook寫下：「這次不來唱寫給別人的歌，而是沒正式發行過，但以前在影片中出現過，現場也偶爾唱過的歌，應該很少人聽過。這首歌叫〈只有可以〉，如果有Monday blue的人，希望聽了可以打起一點精神啊！」而青峰為了幫一班歌迷踢走「Monday Blue」都十分落力，在影片中大放笑彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vy5m9X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vy5m9X&d=vzPM3nPDisIkFtDYl7qxzAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=a50de9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vy5m9X</a>"}]}